import sys
import os
import yaml
import torch
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from datetime import datetime
import pandas as pd

# src 디렉토리를 시스템 경로에 추가
sys.path.append(os.path.abspath('../src'))

# 필요한 클래스들 import
from filter import DroneDataFilter
from model import ModelTrainer

# 설정 파일 로드
with open('../src/config/model_config.yaml', 'r') as f:
    model_config = yaml.safe_load(f)

with open('../src/config/filter_config.yaml', 'r') as f:
    filter_config = yaml.safe_load(f)

try:
    # 1. 데이터 전처리
    print("Initializing data preprocessing...")
    filter = DroneDataFilter(filter_config)
    processed_data, scaler_params = filter.filter_batch()
    print("Data preprocessing completed")
    
    # 데이터 형태 출력
    print("\nProcessed data shape:", processed_data.shape)
    
    # 필요한 특성만 선택하고 numpy array로 변환
    feature_columns = model_config['data']['feature_columns']
    input_data = processed_data[feature_columns].values.astype(np.float32)
    
    print("\nSelected features shape:", input_data.shape)
    print("Data type:", input_data.dtype)
    
    # 2. 모델 학습 준비
    print("\nInitializing model training...")
    trainer = ModelTrainer(model_config)
    train_loader, test_loader = trainer.prepare_data(input_data)
    
    # 3. 모델 학습
    print("\nStarting model training...")
    losses = trainer.train_model(train_loader)
    
    # 학습 곡선 시각화
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    plt.plot(losses)
    plt.title('Training Loss Over Time')
    plt.xlabel('Epoch')
    plt.ylabel('Loss')
    plt.grid(True)
    plt.show()
    
    # 4. 모델 평가
    print("\nEvaluating model...")
    test_loss, predictions, actuals = trainer.evaluate_model(test_loader)
    print(f"Test Loss: {test_loss:.4f}")
    
    # 예측 결과 시각화
    plt.figure(figsize=(15, 6))
    n_samples = 200  # 처음 200개 샘플만 시각화
    
    # IMU 데이터 예측 시각화
    plt.subplot(1, 2, 1)
    plt.plot(actuals[:n_samples, 0], label='Actual IMU')
    plt.plot(predictions[:n_samples, 0], label='Predicted IMU')
    plt.title('IMU Predictions')
    plt.legend()
    
    # Position 데이터 예측 시각화
    plt.subplot(1, 2, 2)
    plt.plot(actuals[:n_samples, -3:], label='Actual Position')
    plt.plot(predictions[:n_samples, -3:], label='Predicted Position')
    plt.title('Position Predictions')
    plt.legend()
    
    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()
    
    # 5. 모델 저장
    print("\nSaving model...")
    trainer.save_model()
    print("Model saved successfully")
    
except Exception as e:
    print(f"Error occurred: {e}")
    print("\nError details:")
    import traceback
    traceback.print_exc()
finally:
    filter.cleanup()
